description:
In this highly-visible role, you will:
- Provide full support for state-of-the-art custom and mixed-signal flows, tool development, installation, and maintenance;;
- Work with the design team to develop utilities and scripts;
- Drive design methodology to increase efficiency;
- Work with the CAD team to provide general CAD services support, utilities, and scripts while also working closely with the Design and Layout teams;
- Support tool configuration and application, as well as build and maintain relevant documentation;
- Support Virtuoso Layout and schematic software and release flows based on the revision control system;
- Involvement in test development, automation, and regression flow support.
